<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idcd809f88-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8" identifier="/us/usc/t47/s32"><num value="32">§ 32.</num><heading> Application</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of this chapter shall be held to apply only to cables to which the convention for the time being applies.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idcd809f89-7553-11f1-8811-da7bbbed8cd8">(<ref href="/us/act/1888-02-29/ch17/s12">Feb. 29, 1888, ch. 17, § 12</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/25/42">25 Stat. 42</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
